Entries.default: "This is a whole lot fancier than what we've seen. Who do you suppose lived here? And when?"
"That seems a little too nice for a place like this."
"Beautiful. It is a good thing pirates did not reach this place before us, or it would have been melted down by now."
"Nowhere in the isles have I seen such craftsmanship..."
"If anyone wants to drag that back to the ship, I'm game."
"Never seen anything so pretty in my life."
"Fascinating. And in remarkable condition, given the surroundings."
